1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:01,600
You idiot!

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,280
What if something happened to you?

3
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:05,400
What's wrong?
Why so sudden?

4
00:00:05,400 --> 00:00:06,080
I'm sorry!

5
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,080
Some creep wouldn't leave me alone.

6
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:13,320
Huh?

7
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:14,320
Kono Mizuki?

8
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:17,120
Thank you.

9
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,160
Iijima Hinata...

10
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,880
I was so scared...

11
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:25,840
Hey, Kono Mizuki?

12
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,320
Kono Mizuki?

13
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,360
Hey!

14
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:32,760
Are you okay?

15
00:00:32,760 --> 00:00:33,760
Kono Mizuki!

16
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:34,760
Hey! Kono Mizuki!

17
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,000
101.3 degrees.

18
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,560
That's a high fever.

19
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,680
No wonder I feel so lightheaded.

20
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,320
I might get you sick.

21
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,840
Stay away from me.

22
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:58,520
No...

23
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,240
Huh?

24
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:04,000
Since we're living together,

25
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,000
we should look out for each other.

26
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,520
Let's get you into some dry clothes first.

27
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,920
Ah...
